{"title":"Angular中的ng-switch指令","slug":"AngularJS中的ng-switch指令","date":"2017-09-20T04:20:54.136Z","updated":"2017-09-20T04:31:26.499Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"ng-switch指令\"><a href=\"#ng-switch指令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ng-switch指令\"></a>ng-switch指令</h2></blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>功能: 对某1个变量的值进行匹配.匹配成功的元素将会被创建.<figure class=\"highlight js\"><div class=\"mdui-table-fluid\"><table class=\"mdui-table mdui-table-hoverable \"><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//js</span></div><div class=\"line\"> <span class=\"keyword\">switch</span>(num)&#123;</div><div class=\"line\">     <span class=\"keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"number\">10</span>:</div><div class=\"line\">         xxx</div><div class=\"line\">         <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">     <span class=\"keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"number\">20</span>:</div><div class=\"line\">         xxx</div><div class=\"line\">         <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</div><div class=\"line\">     <span class=\"keyword\">default</span>:</div><div class=\"line\">         xxx</div><div class=\"line\">         <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</div><div class=\"line\"> &#125;</div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\"> &lt;!-- ------------ --&gt;</div><div class=\"line\"> <span class=\"comment\">//AngularJS</span></div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\"> &lt;body ng-app=<span class=\"string\">\"hmApp\"</span>&gt;</div><div class=\"line\">     &lt;div ng-controller=<span class=\"string\">\"hmCtrl\"</span>&gt;</div><div class=\"line\">         &lt;ul ng-<span class=\"keyword\">switch</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"lesson\"</span>&gt;</div><div class=\"line\">             &lt;li ng-<span class=\"keyword\">switch</span>-when=<span class=\"string\">\"python\"</span>&gt;<span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\">             &lt;li ng-<span class=\"keyword\">switch</span>-when=<span class=\"string\">\"python\"</span>&gt;<span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\">             &lt;li ng-<span class=\"keyword\">switch</span>-<span class=\"keyword\">default</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"python\"</span>&gt;<span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\">         &lt;<span class=\"regexp\">/ul&gt;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"regexp\">     &lt;/</span>div&gt;</div><div class=\"line\"> &lt;<span class=\"regexp\">/bod&gt;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"regexp\"></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"regexp\"> &lt;script&gt;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"regexp\">     var spp = angular.module(\"hmApp\",[]);</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"regexp\">     app.controller(\"hmCtrl\",[\"$scope\",function($scope)&#123;</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"regexp\">         $scope.leson = \"python\"</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"regexp\">     &#125;])</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"regexp\"> &lt;/</span>script&gt;</div></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></li>\n</ul>\n","categories":[{"name":"Angular","path":"api/categories/Angular.json"}],"tags":[]}